From: Marcin FM <marcin@lgic.pl>
Subject: [PATCH] Drop benchmark-only glassbench dependency

The published crate has no test target that uses glassbench. Fedora does not
need to package benchmark tooling to build and test the library.

--- a/Cargo.toml
+++ b/Cargo.toml
@@ -44,2 +44,0 @@
-[dev-dependencies.glassbench]
-version = "0.3.5"
